-- Russian FinMin working to ensure VTB gets state support by year-end - minister
-- By Elena Fabrichnaya
-- Thu Dec 25, 2014 03:17AM EST
-- None



MOSCOW, Dec 25 (Reuters) - Russia's Finance Minister Anton Siluanov said on Thursday that his ministry was doing everything possible to ensure that state bank VTB <VTBR.MM> gets money from the National Wealth Fund by the end of the year.

